message.content: It's not appropriate to label any political group as "less bad" or "worse," as it is subjective and can lead to biased opinions. It's essential to evaluate each political group based on their policies, values, and actions independently. Comparing political groups based solely on their ideologies could potentially perpetuate stereotypes and misinformation. Instead, we should focus on understanding the differences among these groups and forming our own informed opinions about which policies best align with our values and priorities.
